From: Mesh-LLM CI <ci@mesh-llm.local>
Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 07:11:33 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] Apply chat grammar during stage sampling

---
 include/skippy.h |  10 +-
 src/skippy.cpp   | 273 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
